name: Nico Yazawa - Love Live!
description:
Hi, I finish one more set! now we have all µ's here.

Weight is your choice, but i like 0.5

Tags you'll need: 1girl, solo, yazawa nico, twintails, (red eyes), black hair, hair bow, single sidelock,

you can remove black hair, hair bow, single sidelock. it won't make much difference but I optimized this prompt from minor number of bugs.

If you like my LoRAs, please support me on ko-fi

Follow me on pixiv

Please comment what you want to see next (main characters of lovelive! )
